| TDATA7 | TDATA8 |
| TDATA8 | TDATA10 |
| TDATA9 | 0 |
| TDATA10 | TDATA7 |
| TDATA11 | -TDATA2 |
| TDATA12 | 0 |
| TDATA13 | TDATA5 |
| TDATA14 | 0 |
| TDATA15 | 1 |
| TDATA16 | 0 |
| TDATA17 | TDATA9 |
| TDATA18 | TDATA11 |
| TDATA19 | 0 |
| TDATA20 | TDATA7 |
| TDATA31 | TDATA16 |
""" .

